components.cell.typeChecker

Class NullTypeChecker

  • java.lang.Object
    • components.cell.typeChecker.NullTypeChecker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TypeChecker2

    public class NullTypeChecker
extends java.lang.Object
implements TypeChecker2
    The NullTypeChecker class implements the TypeChecker2 interface to handle checking and parsing of objects as NULL types.

    This class provides methods to check if an object is null or an empty string, to get the corresponding CellType, and to parse the object as null. 

     
 NullTypeChecker nullChecker = new NullTypeChecker();
 boolean isNull = nullChecker.check(null);
 CellType cellType = nullChecker.getCellType();
 Object parsedValue = nullChecker.parse(null);
